3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e6dd5981-2840-47cf-9dc2-a11fd4c7b405%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20gel%5C%22%3EBest%20hairball%20gel%20overall%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELubricant-based%20gels%20are%20among%20the%20best%20cat%20hairball%20remedies%20because%20they%20are%20the%20most%20effective%20at%20treating%20and%20preventing%20hairballs.%20Hairball%20gels%20use%20ingredients%20like%20white%20petroleum%2C%20mineral%20oil%2C%20or%20other%20oils%20to%20gently%20help%20hair%20pass%20through%20your%20cat's%20digestive%20tract%20so%20it%20can%20be%20eliminated%20through%20their%20stool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20top%20choice%20for%20hairball%20control%20gel%20is%20Tomlyn%20Laxatone%20Hairball%20Remedy%20Gel.%20It%20carries%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasc.cc%2Fnasc-seal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Animal%20Supplement%20Council%20(NASC)%20quality%20seal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20addition%20to%20safely%20and%20gently%20eliminating%20hairballs%2C%20it%20can%20prevent%20their%20formation%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Laxatone%20hairball%20supplement%20from%20Tomlyn%2C%20that's%20been%20a%20favorite%20of%20mine%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhaywardvethospital.com%2Fteam%2Fdr-keith-w-harper-ii%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Keith%20Harper%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20veterinarian%20and%20owner%20of%20Hayward%20Veterinary%20Hospital%20in%20California.%20%26quot%3BI've%20had%20the%20most%20success%20with%20the%20Laxatone%20over%20my%20career.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETomlyn%20Laxatone%20gel%20provides%20quick%20relief%20with%20a%20blend%20of%20three%20gentle%20lubricants%20(petrolatum%2C%20light%20mineral%20oil%2C%20and%20soybean%20oil)%20in%20three%20different%20flavored%20gels%3A%20catnip%2C%20maple%2C%20and%20tuna.%20Omega-3%2C%206%2C%20and%209%20fatty%20acids%20are%20added%20to%20help%20support%20skin%20and%20coat%20health.%20It's%20easy%20to%20give%3A%20Simply%20squeeze%20a%20small%20amount%20on%20your%20cat's%20nose%20or%20paw%20for%20them%20to%20lick%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf03b208-be8a-429f-9f85-4701ad39d859%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20non-petroleum%20gel%5C%22%3EBest%20non-petroleum%20hairball%20gel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20hairball%20gels%20contain%20white%20petrolatum%2C%20a%20semi-solid%20gel%20derived%20from%20oil%20and%20the%20same%20ingredient%20found%20in%20Vaseline.%20Although%20petrolatum%20is%20a%20safe%20and%20effective%20hairball%20remedy%20recommended%20by%20veterinarians%2C%20some%20pet%20owners%20prefer%20to%20avoid%20petroleum%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20top%20pick%20for%20a%20petroleum-free%20hairball%20gel%20is%20Nutri-Vet%20Hairball%20Paw%20Gel%2C%20which%20uses%20natural%20lubricant%20ingredients%20to%20prevent%20and%20eliminate%20hairballs.%20The%20gel%20consists%20of%20three%20natural%20oils%20(hydrogenated%20vegetable%20oil%2C%20soybean%20oil%2C%20and%20corn%20oil)%20plus%20fiber%20to%20provide%20lubrication%20and%20help%20eliminate%20and%20prevent%20hairballs%20in%20adult%20cats%20and%20kittens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20veterinarian-formulated%20remedy%20also%20contains%20omega-3%20fatty%20acids%20for%20a%20shiny%20coat%20and%20healthy%20skin%20%E2%80%94%20the%20other%20non-petroleum%20hairball%20gel%20we%20considered%20does%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20available%20in%20chicken%20and%20salmon%20flavors%20and%20is%20easy%20to%20give.%20Just%20place%20some%20of%20the%20gel%20on%20your%20cat's%20paw%20for%20them%20to%20lick%20off%20or%20squeeze%20on%20top%20of%20your%20cat's%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e2371fd7-2037-464e-b38d-6adf4b2eb6f3%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20treats%5C%22%3EBest%20hairball%20treats%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHairball%20control%20treats%20are%20a%20good%20option%20for%20cats%20that%20refuse%20to%20take%20hairball%20control%20gels%20because%20they%20don't%20like%20the%20taste.%20Developed%20by%20a%20veterinarian%20for%20hairball%20prevention%2C%20Feline%20Greenies%20Smartbites%20are%20our%20top%20choice%20for%20hairball%20control%20treats%20because%20they%20contain%20two%20effective%20ingredients%3A%20petrolatum%20and%20fiber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmarbites%20are%20loaded%20with%20chicken-based%20protein%20and%20contain%20a%20combination%20of%20plant-based%20fibers%20and%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20petroleum.%20The%20added%20oil%20helps%20lubricate%20the%20digestive%20tract%20to%20minimize%20hairball%20formation%20and%20help%20with%20digestion.%20Available%20in%20both%20chicken%20and%20tuna%20flavors%2C%20each%20treat%20has%20less%20than%202%20calories.%20You%20can%20feed%20a%2010-pound%20cat%20up%20to%2018%20treats%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2225de6f56-9379-4296-8ed7-0a46a4457b10%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20supplement%5C%22%3EBest%20hairball%20supplement%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20supplement%20to%20promote%20healthy%20digestion%20for%20hairball%20prevention%2C%20our%20top%20pick%20is%20Vet's%20Best%20Hairball%20Relief%20Digestive%20Aid%20supplement.%20It%20contains%20three%20types%20of%20ingredients%20to%20support%20digestion%20and%20prevent%20or%20eliminate%20hairballs%3A%20fiber%2C%20probiotics%2C%20and%20multiple%20natural%20ingredients.%20We%20chose%20this%20over%20VetriScience%20Hairball%20Chicken%20Liver%20Flavored%20Soft%20Chews%20Hairball%20Control%20Supplement%20for%20Cats%2C%20which%20only%20contains%20fiber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chews%2C%20made%20from%20all-natural%20plant-based%20ingredients%2C%20including%20marshmallow%20root%2C%20slippery%20elm%20bark%2C%20and%20papaya%20extract%2C%20support%20your%20cat's%20digestive%20system%20and%20help%20prevent%20hairballs.%20This%20supplement%20carries%20the%20National%20Animal%20Supplement%20Council%20(NASC)%20quality%20seal.%20This%20formula%20is%20free%20from%20petroleum-based%20ingredients%20and%20comes%20in%20a%20chicken%20flavor.%20Each%20bottle%20contains%2060%20tablets%20to%20provide%20your%20cat%20a%20full%2030%20days%20of%20hairball%20prevention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chicken-flavored%20chewable%20supplements%20are%20easy%20to%20administer.%20Simply%20break%20the%20tab%20into%20pieces%20to%20entice%20your%20cat%20and%20give%20them%20as%20a%20treat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2205368a48-9ea2-4145-809d-8ba780c9a5cc%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20dry%20hairball%20food%5C%22%3EBest%20dry%20cat%20food%20for%20hairballs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHairball%20control%20cat%20foods%20contain%20extra%20fiber%20to%20help%20prevent%20or%20eliminate%20hairballs.%20Although%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-food-for-hairballs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20hairball%20control%20cat%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20as%20effective%20at%20eliminating%20hairballs%20as%20gel%20remedies%2C%20they%20are%20a%20great%20addition%20to%20a%20prevention%20routine%20and%20useful%20for%20cats%20who%20refuse%20to%20take%20gel%20remedies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIams%20Proactive%20Health%20Indoor%20Weight%20and%20Hairball%20Care%20is%20a%20high-fiber%2C%20budget-friendly%20food.%20Its%20fiber%20blend%20includes%20beet%20pulp%20to%20aid%20in%20digestion%20and%20reduce%20hairballs.%20Added%20omega%20fatty%20acids%20help%20support%20a%20healthy%20coat%20and%20skin%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22986ed8a4-dd8e-40cc-a994-f90940a1834e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20wet%20hairball%20food%5C%22%3EBest%20wet%20cat%20food%20for%20hairballs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHairball%20control%20cat%20foods%20contain%20extra%20fiber%20to%20help%20prevent%20or%20eliminate%20hairballs.%20Dry%20hairball%20foods%20may%20be%20more%20effective%20since%20they%20contain%20more%20fiber%20than%20wet%20formulations.%20However%2C%20for%20cats%20that%20eat%20wet%20food%20only%2C%20Purina%20Pro%20Plan%20Hairball%20Adult%20Wet%20Cat%20Food%20is%20our%20top%20recommendation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20wet%20food%20has%20the%20most%20fiber%20of%20any%20of%20the%20canned%20hairball%20cat%20food%20formulas%20we%20considered.%20It%20also%20contains%20about%2050%25%20more%20than%20Purina's%20popular%20adult%20wet%20food%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110107555bq-20%26h%3Db119783cfa93ff1179ca25740a0c4876dbc44416dd40fbfebb53736ecada0c7f%26postID%3D688938f83d1ce42a6a0d8238%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-cat-hairball-remedies%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.petco.com%252Fshop%252Fen%252Fpetcostore%252Fproduct%252Fpurina-pro-plan-classic-chunky-chicken-entree-adult-wet-cat-food%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EComplete%20Essentials%20Chunky%20Chicken%20Entr%C3%A9e%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20comes%20in%20three%20flavors%3A%20chicken%2C%20turkey%2C%20salmon%2C%20and%20ocean%20whitefish%20and%20tuna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e46887e9-4fb4-41de-8920-4364ccfc1f91%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20hairball%20remedies%20for%20cats%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20cat%20is%20throwing%20up%20hairballs%2C%20make%20an%20appointment%20with%20your%20veterinarian.%20They%20can%20recommend%20which%20hairball%20medicine%20or%20remedy%20might%20be%20appropriate%20for%20your%20cat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20simply%20recommend%20choosing%20the%20remedy%20that%20the%20cat%20is%20most%20likely%20to%20accept%20and%20eat%2C%26quot%3B%20Whittenburg%20says.%20%26quot%3BSome%20cats%20refuse%20the%20treats.%20Some%20cats%20don't%20like%20the%20gel.%20Some%20cats%20won't%20eat%20the%20food%2C%20or%20have%20medical%20conditions%20requiring%20a%20different%20diet.%20All%20the%20remedies%20are%20similar%2C%20but%20the%20delivery%20method%20is%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20which%20hairball%20remedy%20works%20best%20for%20your%20cat%20might%20take%20some%20trial%20and%20error.%20Harper%20says%20it's%20possible%20to%20overdo%20it%20with%20hairball%20remedies%20and%20recommends%20trying%20one%20remedy%20at%20a%20time.%20%26quot%3BIt%20could%20turn%20into%20a%20situation%20where%20the%20cat%20is%20not%20vomiting%20up%20hairballs%2C%20but%20it's%20vomiting%20up%20everything%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20at%20a%20time%20would%20be%20sufficient%20to%20see%20what%20works%20best.%20Otherwise%2C%20you%20won't%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20best%20cat%20hairball%20remedies%20don't%20seem%20to%20be%20helping%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20vet%20for%20a%20follow-up.%20%26quot%3BMore%20diagnostics%20need%20to%20be%20performed%20to%20rule%20out%20more%20serious%20gastrointestinal%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Whittenburg%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20different%20types%20of%20hairball%20remedies%20to%20consider%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHairball%20gels%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHairball%20gels%20are%20given%20daily%20to%20eliminate%20current%20hairballs%20or%20a%20few%20times%20a%20week%20to%20prevent%20hairballs%20from%20forming.%20Most%20over-the-counter%20hairball%20remedies%20contain%20petroleum%20or%20mineral%20oil%2C%20which%20provide%20lubrication%20to%20help%20move%20the%20hair%20through%20your%20cat's%20digestive%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20products%20are%20not%20absorbed%20into%20the%20cat's%20gastrointestinal%20system%20and%20will%20pass%20right%20through%2C%20so%20there%20is%20no%20danger%20posed%20to%20the%20cat's%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20Whittenburg%20says%2C%20emphasizing%20that%20all%20hairball%20products%20should%20be%20given%20according%20to%20the%20directions%20on%20the%20label.%20However%2C%20regular%20grooming%20is%20always%20the%20first%20line%20of%20defense%20for%20avoiding%20hairballs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHairball%20food%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESpecially%20formulated%20hairball%20diets%20contain%20extra%20fiber%20to%20support%20digestive%20health%20and%20help%20push%20hair%20through%20the%20digestive%20tract.%20Both%20dry%20and%20wet%20hairball%20diets%20are%20available.%20Hairball%20foods%20are%20complete%20and%20balanced%20and%20intended%20to%20be%20used%20as%20your%20cat's%20regular%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHairball%20treats%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELike%20hairball%20food%2C%20hairball%20treats%20usually%20contain%20fiber.%20Some%20also%20contain%20lubricating%20ingredients%20like%20petroleum%20or%20other%20oils.%20Treats%20are%20typically%20given%20daily%20%E2%80%94%20follow%20the%20recommendations%20on%20the%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHairball%20supplements%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHairball%20supplements%20are%20not%20intended%20to%20eliminate%20hairballs%20that%20your%20cat%20currently%20has%2C%20but%20they%20contain%20natural%20ingredients%20to%20support%20digestive%20health%20and%20help%20prevent%20future%20hairballs%20from%20forming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef9abe23-9720-46e0-a1b2-8b6ad38d3e89%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20selected%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20selected%20the%20best%20cat%20hairball%20remedies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20researched%20various%20gels%2C%20pills%2C%20treats%2C%20and%20foods%20to%20bring%20you%20our%20top%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20cat%20hairball%20remedies.%20Products%20that%20carry%20the%20National%20Animal%20Supplement%20Council%20(NASC)%20quality%20seal%20are%20rated%20higher%20than%20those%20that%20do%20not.%20NASC-certified%20products%20pass%20a%20comprehensive%20third-party%20audit%20and%20maintain%20ongoing%20compliance%20with%20rigorous%20NASC%20quality%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20additional%20expertise%2C%20we%20interviewed%20two%20veterinarians%20for%20advice%20about%20preventing%20and%20treating%20hairballs%20in%20cats.%20Although%20the%20information%20they%20shared%20contributed%20to%20our%20product%20selection%2C%20our%20veterinary%20experts%20did%20not%20specifically%20endorse%20any%20of%20the%20products%20included%20in%20this%20guide%2C%20unless%20explicitly%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223fa2c626-228e-42e9-9967-69ad57a49313%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3ECat%20hairball%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20do%20cats%20get%20hairballs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECats%20inadvertently%20develop%20hairballs%20when%20they%20groom%20themselves.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20cat%20grooms%2C%20they%20swallow%20some%20of%20the%20loose%20hair%20from%20their%20coat%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpetvetlubbock.com%2Fveterinarians%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Jamie%20Whittenburg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20veterinarian%20and%20owner%20of%20Kingsgate%20Animal%20Hospital%20in%20Lubbock%2C%20Texas.%20%26quot%3BCats%20are%20especially%20prone%20to%20ingesting%20loose%20hair%20because%20they%20have%20spikes%20on%20their%20tongues%20called%20lingual%20papillae.%20The%20hair%20becomes%20caught%20in%20the%20spikes%2C%20and%20the%20cat%20then%20swallows%20it.%26quot%3B%20Since%20cats%20cannot%20digest%20hair%2C%20it%20must%20pass%20through%20the%20digestive%20system%20and%20come%20out%20in%20the%20cat's%20stool.%20However%2C%20sometimes%20hair%20becomes%20trapped%20in%20the%20stomach%2C%20creating%20a%20hairball.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20it%20normal%20for%20cats%20to%20throw%20up%20hairballs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20cats%20can%20develop%20the%20occasional%20hairball.%20Long-haired%20cats%20are%20especially%20prone%20to%20them.%20If%20your%20cat%20gets%20a%20hairball%20occasionally%2C%20it's%20usually%20not%20cause%20for%20alarm.%20But%20if%20your%20cat%20is%20throwing%20up%20hairballs%20frequently%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20a%20month%20normally%20is%20not%20as%20big%20of%20a%20deal%2C%20once%20a%20week%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20too%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20Harper%20says.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20tell%20me%20that%20their%20cat%20vomits%20every%20day%20or%20every%20week%2C%20it's%20a%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20hairballs%20be%20dangerous%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECats%20often%20vomit%20up%20hairballs%20%E2%80%94%20what%20some%20people%20call%20%26quot%3Bcoughing%20up%26quot%3B%20hairballs%20%E2%80%94%20but%20if%20hair%20becomes%20lodged%20in%20the%20small%20intestine%2C%20it%20can%20cause%20a%20life-threatening%20obstruction%2C%20which%20could%20require%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20cat%20that%20is%20vomiting%20or%20retching%2C%20lethargic%2C%20or%20does%20not%20want%20to%20eat%20may%20have%20an%20obstruction%20from%20a%20hairball%2C%26quot%3B%20Whittenburg%20says.%20%26quot%3BDefecating%20does%20not%20rule%20out%20a%20hairball%2C%20as%20feces%20are%20stored%20in%20the%20colon%20and%20intestinal%20obstructions%20occur%20in%20the%20small%20intestine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20should%20you%20do%20if%20your%20cat%20is%20throwing%20up%20hairballs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20make%20an%20appointment%20to%20see%20your%20veterinarian%20if%20you%20suspect%20your%20cat%20is%20having%20an%20issue%20with%20hairballs.%20Harper%20says%20that%20cats%20that%20get%20frequent%20hairballs%20may%20have%20some%20kind%20of%20underlying%20skin%20condition%20causing%20them%20to%20over-groom%20themselves%20and%2C%20as%20a%20result%2C%20develop%20hairballs.%20Red%20rashes%20or%20areas%20with%20very%20short%20hair%20or%20no%20hair%20at%20all%20are%20all%20cause%20for%20concern%20and%20should%20be%20shared%20with%20your%20veterinarian%2C%20explains%20Harper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20checking%20your%20cat%20for%20other%20health%20concerns%2C%20your%20vet%20can%20discuss%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20address%20your%20cat's%20hairballs.%20These%20include%20increasing%20brushing%20with%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-brush%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20cat%20brushes%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20reduce%20how%20much%20hair%20your%20cat%20swallows%20while%20self-grooming%20and%20using%20one%20or%20more%20hairball%20remedies%2C%20such%20as%20a%20hairball%20gel%2C%20food%2C%20treat%2C%20or%20supplement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20can%20you%20prevent%20hairballs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Whittenburg%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20reduce%20hairballs%20is%20through%20daily%20brushing.%20%26quot%3BRemoving%20the%20hair%20before%20the%20cat%20has%20a%20chance%20to%20swallow%20it%20works%20wonders%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Cats%20with%20recurrent%20severe%20issues%20can%20also%20benefit%20from%20shaving%2C%20but%20other%20measures%2C%20like%20hairball%20food%20and%20treatments%2C%20may%20still%20be%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-hairball-remedies%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753826204000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688942393d5881a51c1e3850%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-hairball-remedies%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20cat%20hairball%20remedies%20include%20gels%2C%20treats%2C%20and%20dry%20and%20wet%20food.%20Here%20are%20our%20top%20vet-recommended%20picks%20from%20Tomlyn%2C%20Vet's%20Best%2C%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jlfranza%40yahoo.com%20(Jackie%20Brown%2CSorin%20McKnight)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-hairball-remedies%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shohei%20Ohtani%20Interpreter%20Gambling%20Scandal%20Scripted%20Series%20Nears%20Starz%20Deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753826154000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.c