0California%20judge%20for%20Elon%20Musk's%20racketeering%20lawsuit%20against%20Sam%20Altman%20granted%20the%20Tesla%20CEO%20a%20small%20legal%20victory%20Tuesday%2C%20but%20not%20before%20dinging%20both%20sides%20for%20trying%20to%20waste%20her%20time%20with%20%26quot%3Bexcessive%26quot%3B%20court%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20will%20not%20waste%20precious%20judicial%20resources%20on%20the%20parties'%20gamesmanship%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20District%20Judge%20Yvonne%20Gonzalez%20Rogers%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere%2C%20the%20parties%20to%20this%20action%20have%20repeatedly%20over-litigated%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge's%20terse%2C%20two-page%20decision%20grants%20Musk's%20request%20that%20she%20trim%20Altman's%20bulky%20response%20to%20the%20bulky%2C%202024%20lawsuit%2C%20which%20accuses%20OpenAI%20and%20Microsoft%20of%20civil%20racketeering%2C%20fraud%2C%20breach%20of%20contract%2C%20and%20violating%20antitrust%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman's%20lawyers%20responded%20by%20filing%20a%20list%20of%2055%20%26quot%3Baffirmative%20defenses.%26quot%3B%20(Affirmative%20defenses%20are%20to%20be%20proven%20at%20trial%20by%20the%20defense.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiling%2055%20affirmative%20defenses%20was%20an%20overblown%20response%20on%20Altman's%20part%2C%20Gonzalez%20Rogers%20wrote%20Tuesday%2C%20agreeing%20with%20Musk's%20lawyers%20on%20that%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlaintiffs%20are%20correct%20that%20defendants%20have%20inappropriately%20asserted%20an%20excessive%20number%20of%20defenses%2C%20many%20of%20which%20appear%20to%20be%20irrelevant%2C%20redundant%2C%20insufficient%20or%20immaterial%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Musk's%20lawyers%20answered%20Altman's%20excessiveness%20with%20still%20more%20excess%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20side%20%26quot%3Bfailed%20to%20take%20the%20high%20road%2C%20instead%20moving%20to%20strike%20%3Cem%3Eall%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20assert