%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECorroborating%20this%2C%20a%20NITI%20Aayog%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fmagazine%2Fcover-story%2Fstory%2F20210329-the-great-indian-thirst-1781280-2021-03-20%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520NITI%2520Aayog%2520report%2520in%2Cpose%2520a%2520serious%2520health%2520risk.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20stated%20that%20600%20million%20people%20in%20India%2C%20which%20is%20almost%20half%20its%20population%2C%20face%20extreme%20water%20crises%20every%20day.%20The%20situation%20is%20so%20bad%20that%20almost%20three-fourths%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20households%20have%20to%20rely%20on%20surviving%20on%20dirty%20polluted%20water%20as%20they%20have%20no%20access%20to%20piped%20potable%20water%20in%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20situation%2C%20water%20conservation%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20avert%20impending%20doom.%20However%20in%20pursuit%20of%20solutions%20to%20bolster%20our%20future%2C%20one%20must%20look%20back%20into%20the%20past%20where%20earlier%20civilizations%20have%20battled%20similar%2C%20if%20not%20the%20same%2C%20challenges%20around%20water%20scarcity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20floods%20to%20droughts%2C%20one%20can%20find%20an%20array%20of%20eco-friendly%20and%20sustainable%20traditional%20methods%20of%20water%20conservation%20in%20the%20pages%20of%20history%2C%20that%20have%20not%20only%20saved%20millions%20of%20lives%20but%20have%20also%20stood%20the%20test%20of%20time.%20Almost%20every%20region%20in%20India%20is%20blessed%20with%20these%20homegrown%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F384890%2Fmerino-industries-water-conservation-water-management-ponds-reservoirs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20harvesting%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20conservation%20techniques%20that%20are%20tailored%20to%20fit%20the%20unique%