y%20proven%20method%20for%20mangrove%20plantation%20adopted%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Forest%20Department.%20The%20canal%20design%20features%20a%20deep%20main%20feeder%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FE9KOag0IZt%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FE9KOag0IZt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Supriya%20Sahu%20IAS%20(%40supriyasahuias)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsupriyasahuias%2Fstatus%2F1938806165229707581%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2028%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20How%20they%20did%20it%3A%20Scientific%20design%20meets%20traditional%20knowledge%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA.%20Canal%20network%20design%3A%20Enabling%20natural%20tidal%20flushing%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20challenges%20was%20%3Cstrong%3Erestoring%20natural%20tidal%20flow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20waterlogged%20or%20dry%20zones.%20This%20was%20addressed%20through%20two%20engineering%20models%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFishbone%20Design%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mimicking%20the%20structure%20of%20a%20fish%20skeleton%2C%20this%20model%20creates%20a%20central%20canal%20with%20smaller%20lateral%20canals%20extending%20outward.%20It%20allows%20tidal%20waters%20to%20%3Cstrong%3Eflow%20deep%20into%20mangrove%20areas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20enabling%20proper%20flushing%2C%20salinity%20balance%2C%20and%20seed%20dispersal.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBox%20Design%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20rectangular%20network%20of%20interlinked%20canals%2C%20suitable%20for%20flat%20terrain%20with%20stagnant%20water.%20This%20ensures%20%3Cstrong%3Euniform%20water%20circulation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20reducing%20the%20chance%20of%20stagnation%20or%20salinity%20imbalance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20these%20models%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Eover%20380%20km%20of%20canals%3C%2Fstro